obo:UBERON_0002421  a  owl:Class .

gomodel:SYNGO_3091  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.3: \"Knockdown of ROR2 decreases density and morphological maturation of dendritic spines\"\n\nFig.4: \"Effects of overexpression of wild-type and dominant negative ROR2 constructs on dendritic spine density and morphology\". Experimental description: - \" Primary cultures of hippocampal neurons were prepared according to the protocol described by Brewer et al. (1993). Briefly, hippocampus of 18-d-old Sprague-Dawley rat embryos were dissected ...\"\n- Overexpressed ROR2 is of mouse species: \"The expression vectors pcDNA3-mROR2wt-FLAG, pcDNA3-mROR2ΔCRD-FLAG, pcDNA3-mROR2KD-FLAG and pcDNA3-mROR2ΔCt-FLAG, w...\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
